   "source": [
    "### 1757. Recyclable and Low Fat Products"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b6e020a2-662a-48cf-bc2a-07087dcec673",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Write a solution to find the ids of products that are both low fat and recyclable."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "adf88922-7284-4920-ae58-796e0845b372",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "SELECT \n",
    "  product_id\n",
    "FROM Products\n",
    "WHERE low_fats = 'Y' AND recyclable = 'Y'"
   ]
  }
 ],
